      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, reflecting a history of fastidious ownership. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin appointments, remains in peerless condition. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard used market, offering an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
