    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty\u2014it's been absolutely pampered and still looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition with zero issues, and honestly, it still has that new car feel. I\u2019ve loved every second behind the wheel, but it's time for someone else to enjoy this incredible ride. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next home. Come check it out, you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
