      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I've absolutely babied this car from day one, and it's looking just as gorgeous as the day it rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage, regularly detailed, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 43900.0,
