      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including rod bearing service, VANOS overhaul, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, and the engine's compression ratios are within factory tolerances. A superlative driver\u2019s car for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
